《[[極速快感：臥底風雲|臥底風雲]]》發行後，Black Box就為他下一個作品做準備，當然，開發焦點還是街頭競賽。他們已經盡力引起這款遊戲「可能超越範疇」的時機，<ref name="EG2">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/ea-black-box-doing-secret-nfs-game |title=EA Black Box doing secret NFS game |author=Rob Purchese |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2009-01-30 |accessdate=2009-01-31 |archive-date=2012-07-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69WSgQBNn?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/ea-black-box-doing-secret-nfs-game |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Primotech">{{cite web |url=http://www.primotechnology.com/2009/05/14/criterion-developing-need-for-speed-title-for-release-in-2010/ |title=Criterion Developing Need for Sped Title for Release in 2010 |author=Alex Petraglia |date=2009-05-14 |publisher=Primotech |accessdate=2009-10-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091129054458/http://www.primotechnology.com/2009/05/14/criterion-developing-need-for-speed-title-for-release-in-2010/ |archivedate=2009-11-29 }}</ref><ref name="Keith Munro">{{cite interview |last=Munro |first=Keith |interviewer=Tor Thorsen |title=EA readying Need for Speed threesome |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6203924.html |format=Transcript |program=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2009-01-30 |accessdate=2009-10-21 |archive-date=2012-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211003750/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6203924.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而之後遊戲確定以劇情導向為主題。<ref name="nfs2011">{{cite web |url=http://ca.linkedin.com/pub/rees-savidis/16/868/406 |title=LinkedIn profile |author=Rees Savidis |date=2010-07-02 |accessdate=2010-07-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5qv3iNx3R?url=http://ca.linkedin.com/pub/rees-savidis/16/868/406 |archivedate=2010-07-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="nfs2011-2">{{cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/07/01/need-for-speed-shift-2-black-box-developed-nfs-both-hinted-for/ |title=Need for Speed: Shift 2, Black Box-developed NFS both hinted for 2011 |author=James Ransom-Wiley |date=2010-07-